<i>noun</i>: 확인 [화긴], 확언 [화건], 긍정 [긍ː정] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>확인 [화긴]</dt><br>
<dd>check; affirmation; confirmation; verification</dd><br>
<dd>틀림없이 그러한지를 알아보거나 인정함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of finding out if something is true or admitting that it is true.</dd><br>
<dt>확언 [화건]</dt><br>
<dd>assertion; assurance; affirmation</dd><br>
<dd>틀림없이 그러하다고 말함. 또는 그런 말.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of saying that something is definitely true; or such a remark.</dd><br>
<dt>긍정 [긍ː정]</dt><br>
<dd>affirmation; acknowledgement</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 사실이나 생각이 맞다거나 옳다고 인정함.</dd><br>
<dd>Recognizing that a certain fact or idea is correct or right.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>